c=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰時都唔知自己部電腦中咗招，以為部電腦壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就學識咗原來exe可以好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後都唔敢亂咁開exe<br />\n<br />\n當時中咗招之後好似感染埋我個MSN，之後自動send個病毒出去畀唔同人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以話擴散咗出去，倒返轉頭諗，應該喺我中之前就有人中咗，又係喺自己唔察覺之下由得啲病毒散咗出去，所以我就中咗招<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0774c7f1aa856dd59b38cc751987d0de889901","tid":2111953,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"60秒自動關機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957579962ad82428b95c3fb7463d1881a4db4a18","tid":2111953,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"重左window個排"},{"pid":"6f6412af8ac39be90488202313d1650cc4fc3965","tid":2111953,"uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"btw，自從讀咗IT自己寫program之後先發覺exe可以好容易拎到部電腦嘅所有權限，只要user撳個掣就得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以後尾browser都禁埋java，java好容易有呢個問題，成為瀏覽器漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為如果user確認咗之後可以讀到你部機任何嘢，好似android同iphone撳個權限Yes一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以browser採取嘅方式係唔會主動讀你部腦嘅資料，反而係採用被動式，要你自己去browse file upload上傳去server搞個file，而唔係就咁喺本地度搞，當然electron就另計"},{"pid":"9c3e50c472a4a71aed01dabccaddd6f84c8deb9d","tid":2111953,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"剩係中過呢隻 好似M記exe <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jjcnc.com/uploads/allimg/180210/3-1P210102444N5.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jjcnc.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F180210%2F3-1P210102444N5.jpg&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=f95441cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jjcnc.com/uploads/allimg/180210/3-1P210102444N5.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"153871bdd73cbf81bd0fca4502e618a6a912e2f3","tid":2111953,"uid":298759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"shutdown -a者<br />\n<br />\n當年更新有做好又識關埋service冇中過<br />\n係重裝完先有試過"},{"pid":"72215ebe315cda4d153bcfa41739e84177fbc425","tid":2111953,"uid":72926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:13:49.000Z","msg":"個陣吹到一連上網就會中, 老母抆左lan線 搞到我玩左幾星期彈珠台"},{"pid":"89a4dcddd8fcb473612667a3f5acb8f192dc1402","tid":2111953,"uid":183117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc2279e53d7a4d1eb79f2e9026de9fc0d71344ca","tid":2111953,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"killerjo就中過<br />\n仲成日俾人fake左去3uncles, 2girls1cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abb06f9160d70a5c8f636bbc2fa67daabf5f280","tid":2111953,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85de25cf93e4b88d6408165927444cdb27e18e8e","tid":2111953,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"有，結果要重裝windows，但好快又中過&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係 一入windows 裝番dirver又中"},{"pid":"1164d0d4cbf914f46bd514d05fdc80a3fd9b28f7","tid":2111953,"uid":135866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"千年蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8481b208c11abcde8e9b2191c274a0b6267d263e","tid":2111953,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"中過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.